{"tid":2416632,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"惡俗維基起習家底 創辦人轟官二代篤灰","createTime":"2021-02-21T08:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T11:45:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c9dc04ad3fc5779d8fef471bc8433616f474ca60","tid":2416632,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:19:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210221/XB6W2CPIWFA53N3DUPK5FFNHPQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210221%2FXB6W2CPIWFA53N3DUPK5FFNHPQ%2F&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnad04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=9b46db35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210221%2FXB6W2CPIWFA53N3DUPK5FFNHPQ%2F&h=6e9a240a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210221/XB6W2CPIWFA53N3DUPK5FFNHPQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n惡俗維基起習家底 創辦人轟官二代篤灰<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】境外網站「惡俗維基」早前公開了中共中央總書記習近平、習公主習明澤、姐夫鄧家貴的個人資料，24名成員被集體判刑，曾受查的年輕人害怕「秋後算賬」紛紛逃亡國外。本報訪問家屬、惡俗維基創辦人，以及被捕人的同居伴侶，他們直斥網站的二代站長、官二代顧楊陽是篤灰人，「被捕」後竟無罪釋放。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：辯護律師被「約談」促退出案件<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7,300元賄公安洩密<br />\n<br />\n現年26歲的肖彥銳稱，惡俗維基於2013年創立，高峯時期每日流量達14萬人次，「習近平的個人資料早於2018年底已經公開了，當時是幾個人委託一個警察調查出來，給了他6,000元人民幣（約7,300港元），他就去辦了」。他指出，在公安人口系統搜尋高官個人資料會彈出警報，在操作上會留下紀錄，房間也安裝了攝錄鏡頭，所以這名收錢辦事的警察沒有好下場。肖又說，習明澤的資料早於2019年第一季度已外洩，資料通過國家教育局的系統查出來，當時習明澤的照片打了水印。<br />\n<br />\n2016年惡俗維基已受到社科院關注，一度關閉；2017年，控罪書所提及的「K先生」顧楊陽向肖彥銳拿取惡俗維基的備份，他成為二代實際管理人，肖直指他就是篤灰人。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n廣東茂名警方為何只控訴惡俗維基24人？。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3Sd-MVfD3mhec2JbMA25wjFDHFU=/866x924/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BWT5WLNFHRHHRCWKASCLCZE5Y4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3Sd-MVfD3mhec2JbMA25wjFDHFU%3D%2F866x924%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBWT5WLNFHRHHRCWKASCLCZE5Y4.jpg&h=901cd90f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■肖彥銳怒斥顧楊陽出賣牛騰宇等24人，換取自己獲釋。 受訪者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「主犯」遭打至殘廢禁睡<br />\n<br />\n他說：「國內QQ號都是實名的，抓捕都是惡俗維基的會員，同時也是管理員。」他認為，北京當局出於政治考慮，才把牛騰宇「弄得那麼慘」。牛在2019年8月被帶走，其母稱兒子被打至殘廢、不准睡眠，被迫承認是「主嫌」，去年被重判14年。茂名警方在事件後獲嘉獎，《刑事判決書》寫明法院「不予採納」迫供情節。<br />\n<br />\n26歲的劉家榮（Kevin）是惡俗維基案24名被告之一陳濼安的同居伴侶。被捕時還未成年的陳濼安被控「盜竊罪」和「尋釁滋事罪」，判處。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"f108e3510e89d298b23cbde85ac2496f4b5bcd09","tid":2416632,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:27:03.000Z","msg":"習家起底資料呢？"},{"pid":"777feb8ff7fc9bf7cc287a2f0f0b22a8fb614afb","tid":2416632,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:29:21.000Z","msg":"最慘係被人設局， 4個習明澤消息來源，有3個係被強力部門流出。<br />\n得廣州個過未有人認。"},{"pid":"6c31bbb967cdd1d52e1a258d35f97abd8688ad91","tid":2416632,"uid":72630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"777feb8ff7fc9bf7cc287a2f0f0b22a8fb614afb","tid":2416632,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:29:21.000Z","msg":"最慘係被人設局， 4個習明澤消息來源，有3個係被強力部門流出。<br />\n得廣州個過未有人認。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:30:53.000Z","msg":"擺明裝你彈弓"},{"pid":"73556e595e71089e51b4e2676677e43563a9b8a9","tid":2416632,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:33:44.000Z","msg":"勇者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440c12581d73fd7f60c683cdb4822d587e2c2898","tid":2416632,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03ba6b107a6ed8af6e34a51fb325ef5da06b2ba","tid":2416632,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:37:16.000Z","msg":"中华人民共和国万岁"},{"pid":"a30ed7f5513681e696ef4bb8817c6418a4b9a995","tid":2416632,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:39:10.000Z","msg":"強力部門非常強力"},{"pid":"d0bcd5249410fb376e3e7f6ae20dd2073bff3e42","tid":2416632,"uid":156891,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:40:19.000Z","msg":"咁撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依d內部資料一定Trace到架啦，重要查自己老板點會唔知<br />\n<br />\n更戇鳩係點解低級公安會有Authority睇國家主席資料<br />\n<br />\n支那人做野都係斷鳩估、求撚其<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa078706f1b95939663f4f91e4bf922c80f4d86","tid":2416632,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea6c6139d4da89730d56d5052c55317bbf3be30","tid":2416632,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}